data.description: 3 bed, 2 bed house nestled on private 1.64 acres waiting for you to make it your own! Enjoy cozy winter evenings with the wood fireplace that heats the whole home and use the enclosed hot tub to relax after a long day. In the summer, you'll love all the flowers that bloom throughout the property and you can enjoy the grapes and plum, apple, cherry and pear trees that give you more fruit than you can eat! And don't miss the private trail down to Lacamas Creek. Playhouse and playset stay with the home. The chicken coop and greenhouse  are perfect for the homesteader! Plenty of room on the property for all your projects, animals or whatever you can imagine!
